<symbol type="1" id="14" code="109" name="Small knoll"><description>An obvious mound or knoll which cannot be drawn to scale with a contour.
Minimum height: 1 m.
The symbol shall not touch or overlap contours.
Footprint: 7.5 m x 7.5 m.</description><point_symbol inner_radius="375" inner_color="8" outer_width="0" outer_color="-1" elements="0"/></symbol>
<symbol type="1" id="15" code="110" name="Small elongated knoll"><description>An obvious elongated knoll which cannot be drawn to scale with a contour.
Minimum height: 1 m.
The symbol shall not touch or overlap contours.
