<symbol type="1" id="126" code="512.1" name="Bridge / tunnel, minimum size"><description>Bridges and tunnels are represented using the same basic symbols.
If it is not possible to get through a tunnel (or under a bridge), it shall be omitted.
Minimum length (of baseline): 0.4 mm (footprint 6 m).
